Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ドキドキハラハラ こんなのはじめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまで私の 気持ちをもてあそぶの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,無視無視ムリムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,突然始まる 大スペクタクル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あっと言わせる為に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,すべてを 賭けてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,每日 大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,お気楽マイペース男の子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:29.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,とぼけた顔してもダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,だけど つい見ちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:38.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のこと 気になって！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今度は何にするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:43.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,やめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}緊張兮兮 神經兮兮 從來沒試過這種感受的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}你要玩弄人家的感情到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}無視無視 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}突然開始的大奇觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}動員自己的一切腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}就是為了讓我大喊一聲「啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每天都搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}你這個不安分又特立獨行的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:29.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一臉無辜的表情也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}絕對在搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}不過又忍不住看過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:42.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}好在意 你這次又搞什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:43.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}不要啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這裏就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是受詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這裏要加that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紙條？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天還真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,530)\shad0\bord0\c&H1F2123&}第7節課 傳紙條
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小山般的量怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣才能收集到那麼多紙條啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 關君你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 寄給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟真的信一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,from橋野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香寄來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 留美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎 這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在關君開了郵局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳到關君那裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說會被按上郵戳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在上課時干蠢事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不明白哪裏有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我等著你的回信哦 友香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個班級都被他帶進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要好好說說他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to關君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課期間請再認真點。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很困擾！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,from橫井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意 郵寄物品不接受指定規格以外的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連尺寸都規定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公務員態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連那種地方都要再現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橫4厘米豎3厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這樣就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請確認希望的郵寄方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速達 普通 其他班級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指定時間郵寄…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵寄完畢後的通知信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要 不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太詳細了吧 怎樣都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵寄方式是普通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指定時間是現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}本日的窗口業務已結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道我要寄信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼就不能多等我一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一臉臭屁 你以為你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外業務時間以外的郵寄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請利用教室後面的投遞郵箱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 連郵箱都設置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君太亂來了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且連班級外都網羅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服務很周到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就會變成have to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跟動詞的原形…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠 夠不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是上課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這樣 這樣辛苦寄出的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我好好理解我每天是有多困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有回收郵箱裏面的信就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的關君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君一大早嘗嘗不爽的滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此番行動為同班所目擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了奇怪的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此時的橫井同學還未知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課小動作

